       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    ARI29108.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA ARI29108.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Informacao Perfis                                          *
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE ARI29108         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD2000 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD3000 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD1000 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD0200 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY ARCV2910.
       COPY ARCV2911.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0010.
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY ARCK0001.
       COPY ARCK0002.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-ARVT2002 PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARVT2002'.
           05 CON-ARVT1000 PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARVT1000'.
           05 CON-ARVT0200 PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARVT0200'.
           05 CON-ARVT3000 PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARVT3000'.
           05 WS-PROGNAME  PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARI29108'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-NULL                       PIC S9(04) BINARY.
           05 WS-TOTAL-PERFIS               PIC S9(02) VALUE ZEROES.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE ARI29108         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-PROGRAMA    ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO ARCV2910-MSG.
           MOVE ARCV2910-ASE               TO ARCV2911-ASE.
      *
           PERFORM 1100-VALIDACOES
              THRU 1199-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1100-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1100-VALIDACOES.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1100-VALIDACOES  ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      * Năo é permitido eliminar o perfil master da VIA
           IF ARCV2911-INDPERFM EQUAL ARCK0002-PERFILMAST-VIA
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO  TO ARCV2911-CPERFIL-S
              MOVE ARCK0002-CAPLIC-AR      TO ARCV2911-CPERFIL-CAPLIC
              MOVE ARCK0001-OPER-N-PERMITIDA
                                           TO ARCV2911-CPERFIL-MSG
           END-IF.

      * Temos de ter sempre um perfil navegável no portal da VIA e
      * e no portal do cliente
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS AND
           ARCV2911-INDPERFM EQUAL ARCK0002-N-PERFIL-MASTER

              MOVE ARCV2911-INDPERFM       TO ARCD2000-INDPERM
              EXEC SQL
                 SELECT  COUNT(CPERFIL)
                 INTO :WS-TOTAL-PERFIS :WS-NULL
                 FROM  ARVT2002_INFPERFIL
                 WHERE INDPERM = :ARCD2000-INDPERM
              END-EXEC

              MOVE CON-ARVT2002            TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME

              PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
                 THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT

              IF DB2-OK
                 IF WS-TOTAL-PERFIS > 1
                    CONTINUE
                 ELSE
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                                           TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                   MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                           TO ARCV2911-CPERFIL-S
                   MOVE ARCK0002-CAPLIC-AR TO ARCV2911-CPERFIL-CAPLIC
                   MOVE ARCK0001-OPER-N-PERMITIDA
                                           TO ARCV2911-CPERFIL-MSG
                 END-IF
              ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2    TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
              END-IF
           END-IF.

      *    ve se ha utilizadores com o perfil

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE ARCV2910-CPERFIL           TO ARCD3000-CPERFIL

              EXEC SQL
                    SELECT GUSERNAME
                       INTO :ARCD3000-GUSERNAME
                    FROM ARVT3000_PERFISUSER
                    WHERE   CPERFIL = :ARCD3000-CPERFIL
              END-EXEC

              MOVE CON-ARVT3000               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME

              PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
                 THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT

                 IF DB2-OK
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                                           TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                           TO ARCV2911-CPERFIL-S
                    MOVE ARCK0002-CAPLIC-AR
                                           TO ARCV2911-CPERFIL-CAPLIC
                    MOVE ARCK0001-PERFIL-UTILIZADOR
                                           TO ARCV2911-CPERFIL-MSG
                 END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
       1199-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.


           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROGRAMA    ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ARCV2910-ADE               TO ARCV2911-ADE.

      * ELIMINA DA TABELA DOS PEFIS  INFPERFIS
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-ELIMINA-DADOS
                 THRU 2299-ELIMINA-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

      * ELIMINA DA TABELA DOIS DOS PERFIS
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2300-ELIMINA-DADOS
                 THRU 2399-ELIMINA-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

      * ELIMINA DA TABELA DEZ PERFIL ACTIONS
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2400-ELIMINA-DADOS
                 THRU 2499-ELIMINA-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

      * ELIMINA DA TABELA 30  PERFILUSER
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2500-ELIMINA-DADOS
                 THRU 2599-ELIMINA-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2200-ELIMINA-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-ELIMINA-DADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2200-ELIMINA     ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ARCV2910-CPERFIL           TO ARCD2000-CPERFIL

           EXEC SQL
                 DELETE FROM
                ARVT2002_INFPERFIL
                 WHERE
                    CPERFIL = :ARCD2000-CPERFIL
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-ARVT2002               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-NOTFND
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO ARCV2911-CPERFIL-S
                    MOVE ARCK0001-CPERFIL-N-EXISTS
                      TO ARCV2911-CPERFIL-MSG
              ELSE
                 IF NOT DB2-OK
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           ELSE
              MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2       TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
           END-IF.

       2299-ELIMINA-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2300-ELIMINA-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2300-ELIMINA-DADOS.

           MOVE ARCV2910-CPERFIL           TO ARCD0200-CPERFIL

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2300-ELIMINA     ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
                 DELETE FROM
                 ARVT0200_PERFIL
                 WHERE
                    CPERFIL = :ARCD0200-CPERFIL

           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-ARVT0200               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF NOT DB2-OK AND NOT DB2-NOTFND
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                   TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2399-ELIMINA-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2400-ELIMINA-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2400-ELIMINA-DADOS.


           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2400-ELIMINA     ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ARCV2910-CPERFIL           TO ARCD1000-CPERFIL

           EXEC SQL
                DELETE FROM
                ARVT1000_PERFIL_ACTIONS
                WHERE CPERFIL = :ARCD1000-CPERFIL
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-ARVT1000               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF NOT DB2-OK AND NOT DB2-NOTFND
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                   TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
              END-IF
           ELSE
              MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
           END-IF.

       2499-ELIMINA-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2500-ELIMINA-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2500-ELIMINA-DADOS.
      *

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2500-ELIMINA     ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ARCV2910-CPERFIL           TO ARCD3000-CPERFIL

           EXEC SQL
                 DELETE FROM
                ARVT3000_PERFISUSER
                 WHERE   CPERFIL = :ARCD3000-CPERFIL
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-ARVT3000               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF NOT DB2-OK AND NOT DB2-NOTFND
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                   TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
              END-IF
           ELSE
              MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2       TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
           END-IF.


       2599-ELIMINA-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-PROGRAMA    ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ARCV2911-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE ARCV2911-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE ARCV2911-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0010.
           COPY VIAP0016.
